          "description": "I have been going here for about a year now. It\u2019s a great place with great people. Everyone genuinely cares and does their best to take care of you. The clinic is clean, and the staff are very kind and professional. Dr. Vanderveen is one of the best primary care doctors I have ever met. He always makes sure I am well taken care of and always receive the proper treatment.",
