          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8S6I1yct5347Z3RQ7iTMcWQg_qvNQWkkViJHKzx-gpRGj26U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "My doctor Neil Pasco is outstanding and goes above and beyond and his nurse is 5 stars but unfortunately my appointment on 7/25/25 at 11 was not nice all of the female desk agents on the 4th floor of 26st in Manhattan was unpleasant and unprofessional but there was a shining star the one male desk agent he was calm and went above and beyond to help me. He was also 5 stars along with my doctor and nurse.  While it's true a few bad apples can spoil a bunch . This time those few good ones made my day! I have a update to this review. This union health center responded to my review and asked me to call and speak to a supervisor. I called and had to leave a message with a desk receptionist and a message will be returned.  that was yesterday 8/20/25 this morning 8/21/25  a supervisor named Louis Carrasco called me this morning I was sleep and when I woke I called back and once again I had to leave a message for the supervisor lol phone tag !  But this center is overall 5 stars and these 5 star centers should be duplicated. Hopefully when I return a better experience will be had. Update 9/2/25 I want to thank supervisor Louis Carrasco for responding and professionally and thoughtfully handling my issue. once again 5 stars for the 5 star center!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kUWRVVldSR1I1VlZaNldVZE1XV2hGUkVWaVEyYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x2b7a4533c78299b1!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOndQdUVWRGR5VVZ6WUdMWWhFREViQ2c%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "Edited 9 months ago",
