          "description": "Literally the best pcp ive ever had. The people here are really nice and treat patients well. They see you pretty quickly once you arrive for your appointment, and Ive never had to wait more than 10 minutes to be seen in the last 3-4 years ive been coming here. I hate commuting but I happily commute my hour long ride on the train to get here.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSd1ZHaDNOa0pvVm5vMk16TmhhMmRwZFcwM2RGRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x2b7a4533c78299b1!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlRwVGh3NkJoVno2MzNha2dpdW03dFE%7C%7C?hl=en",
