          "description": "Absolutely ridiculous. I have tried to have a therapy consultation three times now. First time was cancelled. Okay no problem, rescheduled. Therapist never called me. I call the center, my phone number is wrong in their system\u2026 even though they called me to reschedule the first time. Whatever, I really need counseling, so I reschedule again for this morning. The therapist did not call again. I will not be looking for care from this clinic any longer- although even if I wanted to, I\u2019m not sure they\u2019d provide it.",
